        "content": "DISABLED TEST MODE\n\nReplace placeholders only inside n8n credentials/environment:\n<APP_URL>\n<AUTOMATION_API_TOKEN>\n<RSS_FEED_URL>\n\nLaravel remains the source of truth. This workflow creates review drafts only.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 360
      },
      "id": "ad3e5f56-6f24-48d5-8a6d-2b875d30f8a0",
